assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Mitsubishi Logisnext Co., Ltd. designs, develops, manufactures, and sells electric and engine-powered forklifts, transportation robots, automated warehouses, electric vehicles, monorails, and LAN and other logistics equipment in Japan. It offers large IC trucks, small and medium sized IC trucks, reach trucks, electric counter balanced trucks, power pallet trucks, order pickers, low lifters, stackers, multi-directional trucks, lateral stacking trucks, towing tractors, and skid steer loaders. Mitsubishi Logisnext Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1937 and is headquartered in Nagaokakyo, Japan.
